HEADWORD: Chronopher
<hw>Chron"o*pher</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ time +
<?/ to carry.]</ety> <def>An instrument signaling the correct time to
distant points by electricity.</def>⟦br⟧
